text: Blagojče Trajkovski (Macedonian: Благојче Трајковски; born 6 October 1986) is a Macedonian handball player who plays for RK Eurofarm Pelister and the Macedonian national team.EHF profile2017 World Championship roster ==References== Category:Living people Category:Macedonian male handball players Category:1986 births Category:Sportspeople from Prilep
title: Blagojče Trajkovski
